From this week, developers around the world could create their own decentralized apps with the tools available on the Inrupt website.
Berners-Lee said his team is not talking to Facebook and Google about whether they will introduce or not a radical change where all their business models are completely modified from one day to the next.
“We’re not going to ask permission.”
